original_title: ‘可愛すぎる！！’と話題のSOD女子社員 宣伝部 桜井彩 超高級ソープ嬢に挑戦！！
overview: Aya Sakurai is the first SOD female employee to challenge the popular project 'Luxury Soapland Lady'! ! Plenty of recordings, from polite lectures by instructors to practical sessions full of super-rich close-up services. Everything you see is unknown, such as a chair, a mat, a washing pot, and a motorcycle... I'm embarrassed to talk to the camera subjectively, but I will do my best to entertain you.
title: Too Cute!! Trending Soft On Demand Girl Super High-Class Soapland Lady. Aya Sakurai Tries Out Being An Ultra High Class Soapland Lady!!
